    <div class="simple-lesson-intro">
        <img src="/assets/images/cryptography-intro.png" alt="Cryptography concept illustration" class="lesson-image">
        <p>Cryptography is a way to keep information safe by turning it into secret code. Only people with the right "key" can read it. The word comes from Greek, meaning "hidden writing."</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="simple-concept-box">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Key Idea</h4>
